-- TUI Expects $86 Million in Interest Next Month as Hapag-Lloyd Refinances
-- B y   M i k e   G a v i n
-- 2010-09-22T06:55:47Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-09-22/tui-foresees-87-million-in-interest-income-after-hapag-lloyd-refinancing.html
TUI AG said that as a result of
planned refinancing transactions of Hapag-Lloyd AG it expects an
inflow of about 65 million euros of deferred interest next
month. TUI also said Hapag-Lloyd will be in “a position to make
interest and redemption payments on the existing financing
instruments rendered to Hapag-Lloyd.”  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Mike Gavin at 
 mgavin2@bloomberg.net  